room_title: Escape room "Kraken the Case" by Zero Hour Escape Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We went for the first time on Saturday. It was a quality made game. The Changes in Latitude room was an original idea. With well thought-out clues. The props made the room and immersive experience. I liked having a screen to support us rather than just an employee in the room, which we experienced at another venue. We needed 3/4 clues from the staff and we didn't escape. But we still had a great time. We look forward to going back again.
